<h1 id="blockchain-transactions">Blockchain transactions</h1>

<h2 id="mana-transfer">MANA Transfer</h2>

<p>A simple scene that uses the MANA smart contract and the EthConnect library to send the player MANA on the Ropsten test network.</p>

<p><a href="https://github.com/decentraland-scenes/MANA-Transaction">Code</a></p>

<p><a href="https://mana-transaction-jfsdmqqnmp.now.sh">Explore the scene</a></p>

<h2 id="mana-burning-altar">MANA Burning Altar</h2>

<p>Fees collected by the Marketplace are stored in a wallet. This scene interacts with the MANA contract to burn this MANA that was collected.</p>

<p>The flame is created as a particle system, handling various entities that spiral around as they change colors.</p>

<p><img src="/images/media/example-mana-altar.png" alt="" /></p>

<p><a href="https://github.com/decentraland-scenes/MANA-Burning-Altar">Code</a></p>

<p><a href="https://mana-altar-nmfgwmfbjo.now.sh">Explore the scene</a></p>

<h1 id="advanced">Advanced</h1>

<h2 id="block-dog">Block Dog</h2>

<p>A scene with a simple AI character. It randomly chooses what action to take: follow you, sit or remain idle. You can also tell it to sit or stand up by clicking it, or tell it to drink water by clicking its bowl.</p>

<p><img src="/images/media/example-blockdog.png" alt="" /></p>

<p><a href="https://github.com/decentraland-scenes/Block-dog">Code</a></p>

